10:00.049 --> 10:01.549
The boys really kept
it up, didn't they?

10:01.550 --> 10:04.052
I used to think a lot
about this place.

10:04.053 --> 10:06.055
I was afraid
it might change,

10:06.555 --> 10:07.556
