beautiful.

10:08.057 --> 10:09.058
Now, this is for me.

10:09.558 --> 10:10.558
You're not going
to stay here.

10:10.559 --> 10:12.060
Why not? I got
a roof over my head,

10:12.061 --> 10:13.062
