in Kahala and a family.

10:16.565 --> 10:18.566
Look, let's get this
over with.

10:18.567 --> 10:20.068
All the time
I was overseas,

10:20.069 --> 10:22.570
I got a letter from
my folks every week

10:22.571 --> 10:24.572
