of my beautiful home

10:24.573 --> 10:26.074
and my beautiful future

10:26.075 --> 10:28.076
in my dad's beautiful
pineapple business.

10:28.077 --> 10:29.577
And the more
they reminded me,

10:29.578 --> 10:31.579
the more I knew
I couldn't come back

10:31.580 --> 10:33.581
with the rest of my life
all laid out for me.

10:33.582 --> 10:34.582
No, Maile.

10:34.583 --> 10:36.584
It's too easy to fall
into a ready-made setup.

10:36.585 --> 10:38.586
I got to do this
on my own. I got to do it myself.

10:38.587 --> 10:40.088
Can't you
tell them that?

10:40.089 --> 10:41.589
- I will!
- Good!

10:41.590 --> 10:43.091
