is right.

10:43.092 --> 10:46.094
Please don't
take too much time.

10:46.095 --> 10:48.596
I don't know how long
I can wait for you to grow up.

10:48.597 --> 10:50.098
Oh, you're
a pretty fresh kid.

10:50.099 --> 10:53.101
