young lady.

20:27.098 --> 20:27.598
Have a nice time.

20:28.099 --> 20:28.599
Thank you.

20:29.100 --> 20:30.601
Come back
and see us.

20:30.602 --> 20:31.603
Bye.

20:33.104 --> 20:34.105
Hello, Mr. Gates.

20:34.606 --> 20:36.106
Hello, Maile.

20:36.107 --> 20:37.608
I'll come right
to the point.

20:37.609 --> 20:38.609
Is my son here?

20:38.610 --> 20:40.110
Chad? Here?

20:40.111 --> 20:41.612
You know what I mean.

20:41.613 --> 20:43.113
I've heard he's been
home for several days.

20:43.114 --> 20:45.115
If this is true, I know
that you've seen him.

20:45.116 --> 20:47.618
Well?

20:47.619 --> 20:49.119
That's good enough
for me.

20:49.120 --> 20:51.121
Chad's mother doesn't
know about this,

20:51.122 --> 20:54.124
